parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission slipping and failure can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded. This can also lead to costly repairs and potentially cause damage to other components.
symptoms: The transmission slips or hesitates when shifting
the engine RPMs suddenly increase
the vehicle loses power
the transmission makes loud noises or grinding sounds
the vehicle is unable to move or is stuck in one gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transfer case disengagement can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded. This can also lead to costly repairs and potentially cause damage to other components.
symptoms: The transfer case disengages without warning
the vehicle loses power
the transmission makes loud noises or grinding sounds
the vehicle is unable to move or is stuck in one gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The air bag sensor failure can cause the air bag system to malfunction, leading to potentially fatal accidents.
symptoms: The air bag light illuminates on the instrument panel
the air bag system fails to deploy in the event of an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The corrosion and failure of brake lines can cause brake failure, leading to accidents, injuries, and fatalities. This is a critical safety issue, as brakes are essential for stopping the vehicle.
symptoms: Brake pedal goes to the floor
brake failure
sudden loss of braking ability
rusted or corroded brake lines
brake lines detaching from the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the airbag system can lead to failure of the airbags to deploy in the event of an accident, which can result in serious injury or fatality.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is on or flashing
the airbag warning message appears on the dashboard
the airbag system is inoperative
the airbag light turns off temporarily and then returns
the airbag light is intermittent.
